      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Customers say

      Customers find this water bottle superior to plastic alternatives and appreciate its ability to keep water cold for extended periods. They like its design, particularly the white leopard pattern, and its size, noting it's perfect for carrying around and fits well in cup holders and backpack side pockets. The bottle receives positive feedback for its color options and durability, though some report durability issues with the handle breaking within a month. The leak resistance receives mixed reviews, with some saying it doesn't leak while others report spilling issues.
